\begin{highlights}
\item Hybrid LLM+calculator architecture achieves Kendall's $\tau = 0.80$ and 83\% Top-1 accuracy across 100 household energy scenarios.
\item Pure Prompting produces near-random rankings ($\tau = -0.06$), demonstrating that standalone LLMs cannot replicate MAVT-based MCDA.
\item Hybrid uses the fewest tokens (98,016) and lowest latency (275.6s), making it both the most accurate and most efficient architecture.
